name: RTCDTMFSender
description: The RTCDTMFSender interface provides a mechanism for transmitting DTMF codes on a WebRTC RTCPeerConnection. You gain access to the connection's RTCDTMFSender through the RTCRtpSender.dtmf property on the audio track you wish to send DTMF with.
